Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒來拜訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的形勢恐怕會很嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以趁有機會 先來見二位一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒想到 你居然還記得父親母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是問題所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心想或許能夠說服你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再像從前那樣賭氣了行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 哥哥已經是我的敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 看來你已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 早就下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天還是就此作罷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福勒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 雷納德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 泰蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及那位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 我們撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是Gebo-9 正降落至Golf地點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-7請做好銜接準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-7 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 相良中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知現在已臨近第三學期了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
